34:27.251 --> 34:30.668
<i>God, how I love you.</i>

34:31.708 --> 34:35.168
<i>I cannot...</i>

34:39.043 --> 34:42.751
<i>embrace...</i>

34:44.458 --> 34:48.208
<i>so much happiness,</i>

