People here in Colombia

35:15.126 --> 35:18.793
have been chewing coca leaves since
the beginning of time.

35:19.084 --> 35:23.209
Pablo is just exporting
a national product.

35:24.043 --> 35:27.126
Most of the money he makes
goes to the poor.

35:27.834 --> 35:31.168
You go to any of the barrios
and ask the people there:

35:32.793 --> 35:34.084
they love him.

35:36.251 --> 35:39.126
Come on. Dance with me.

36:01.126 --> 36:03.084
I'm sorry Nick, did I wake you?

36:03.376 --> 36:04.584
It's ok.

36:08.668 --> 36:11.001
Maria wanted us to talk.

36:11.751 --> 36:15.793
She's been going:
"Tio Pablo. Nick this, Nick that."

36:15.959 --> 36:17.459
"Nick, Nick, Nick..."

36:18.959 --> 36:20.876
"Nick this, Nick that."

36:25.543 --> 36:27.543
ls everything ok? ls your room ok?

36:27.709 --> 36:29.584
Yeah. Yeah it's great. Thank you.

36:31.293 --> 36:34.459
So Maria tells me that your brother
lives at the beach?

36:34.626 --> 36:36.209
And what does he do there?

36:36.376 --> 36:38.626
He has a small business,

36:39.751 --> 36:41.126
they serve food and drinks,

36:41.293 --> 36:44.709
and I give surfing lessons.
