36:45.126 --> 36:46.209
- Ah, it's nice.
-Yeah...

36:47.959 --> 36:49.168
That's nice.

36:50.501 --> 36:51.459
That's nice.

36:54.459 --> 36:57.001
Nick? Do you believe in God?

36:58.168 --> 37:00.084
Yes.

37:00.543 --> 37:01.793
That's good.

37:02.626 --> 37:04.501
Do you take drugs?

37:05.293 --> 37:08.834
No. No I mean, it's not really for me.

37:09.793 --> 37:10.834
That's good.

37:12.209 --> 37:16.334
I've seen drugs eat the souls
of many great men.

37:20.543 --> 37:21.584
Well, listen, Nick.

37:22.959 --> 37:27.084
I just wanted to say that Maria
is like a daughter to me

37:28.501 --> 37:31.043
and we're very happy
if she's found a good match.

37:31.918 --> 37:33.168
Good.

37:33.626 --> 37:34.793
That's good.

37:37.709 --> 37:39.084
Are you serious about her?

37:39.834 --> 37:41.209
Yeah, absolutely.

37:42.668 --> 37:44.084
Do you love her?

37:45.376 --> 37:47.668
- Yeah. More than anything.
-Good.

37:49.751 --> 37:51.001
True love.

37:52.251 --> 37:53.334
True love.

37:53.793 --> 37:54.876
That's the best.

37:55.626 --> 37:57.543
True love.

38:00.793 --> 38:03.959
Good.
So what happened to your arm?

38:05.709 --> 38:07.293
I got attacked by a dog.

38:11.126 --> 38:12.793
That's a big dog.

38:12.959 --> 38:14.293
What happened?

38:14.626 --> 38:17.709
Just some locals... They wanted us
to pay to be on the beach

38:17.876 --> 38:19.793
and we didn't give in.

38:22.168 --> 38:24.043
- And that was their dog?
-Yeah.

38:28.543 --> 38:31.001
Nick, did you like this song
I sang to my wife tonight?

38:32.709 --> 38:35.001
Yeah, that was great.

38:35.168 --> 38:37.543
I didn't understand all of it,
but it was beautiful.

38:38.876 --> 38:41.376
<i>-L'll</i> get a translation.
- Perfect.

38:43.418 --> 38:45.876
Maybe one day you'll sing it to Maria?

38:46.543 --> 38:48.126
In front of all your friends.

38:49.334 --> 38:50.584
Maybe.

38:51.459 --> 38:53.043
We had a good talk.

38:53.209 --> 38:53.876
Yeah.

38:55.043 --> 38:56.334
Get some rest.

38:56.876 --> 38:58.501
I'll see you in the morning.

39:03.959 --> 39:07.084
- Good night.
-Good night.

39:14.126 --> 39:17.668
Light, camera, action!

39:38.834 --> 39:40.751
Kiss again.

39:52.001 --> 39:55.126
Nick and Maria will soon be married

39:55.293 --> 39:59.293
and they will give
many babies to their family.

39:59.918 --> 40:01.584
Right, Nick?

40:01.751 --> 40:03.751
Yep. Yep. Hopefully.

40:05.501 --> 40:06.501
You'd better be fast

40:06.668 --> 40:09.501
or we'll extradite you back to Canada.

40:10.876 --> 40:13.959
Now a big round of applause

40:14.418 --> 40:18.084
to the new member
of the Escobar Gaviria family.

40:18.251 --> 40:20.168
Come on.

40:42.251 --> 40:44.543
<i>Did you tell Escobar</i>

40:44.709 --> 40:46.293
<i>anything about the Roldano Brothers?</i>

40:47.959 --> 40:50.209
They were killed. Two days ago.

40:50.376 --> 40:52.668
They were hung upside down
and burned alive.

40:53.959 --> 40:57.834
Everyone in town is saying
that Escobar and his men did it.

41:05.709 --> 41:07.126
It's not true, brother.

41:09.126 --> 41:11.334
He would never do something like that.

41:12.459 --> 41:14.709
He offered me a job at the Hacienda.

41:14.876 --> 41:16.209
Wait, he did what?

41:16.918 --> 41:19.001
I want you to be happy for me, ok?

41:20.209 --> 41:21.209
Nick.

41:21.834 --> 41:24.959
Nick, you've gotta listen to me
on this one...

41:26.209 --> 41:26.876
Nick!

41:33.376 --> 41:35.668
- Good morning, Carmen.
-Good morning, Nick.

41:35.834 --> 41:38.084
- Daniela.
-Good morning, Nick.

41:59.751 --> 42:01.334
Good morning.

42:14.168 --> 42:16.168
Keep going. Keep going.

42:17.876 --> 42:18.918
- Are you tired?
-Yes.

42:19.084 --> 42:19.834
- Yes?
-Yes.

42:20.001 --> 42:21.251
Nico, come!

42:21.418 --> 42:24.709
- No, buddy. I can't.
-Look at his face.

42:24.876 --> 42:26.126
He's dead, Luis.

42:26.293 --> 42:27.293
There you go.

42:27.793 --> 42:28.834
- Yeah.
-I don't want to.

42:29.001 --> 42:30.293
It's your turn.

42:31.084 --> 42:32.418
Okay.

42:32.918 --> 42:34.251
Luis, get ready!

42:44.793 --> 42:46.168
What are you doing? It's sunday.

42:46.543 --> 42:48.793
That's ok,
I'm just grabbing the pony for Luis.

42:48.959 --> 42:50.376
Nick,
there's no one there to help you!

42:50.543 --> 42:51.876
It's ok, I can do it.

43:22.751 --> 43:23.918
Watch out!

43:25.834 --> 43:28.584
- Who's that?
-Nick. Maria's boyfriend.

43:38.168 --> 43:39.459
Finish it off.

43:56.751 --> 43:59.334
At last we meet, Nick.
It's a pleasure.

44:01.376 --> 44:03.001
My name is Drago Gutierrez,

44:03.168 --> 44:04.751
I work for <i>el</i> patron too.

44:05.876 --> 44:07.709
I know Maria
since she was a little kid.

44:11.876 --> 44:13.043
Everything okay?

44:14.084 --> 44:15.918
Yeah. Yeah, I'm fine.

44:16.501 --> 44:17.251
Look at me.

44:28.251 --> 44:31.959
Bambi, get me the boss.
We have a problem.

44:45.418 --> 44:47.251
You know who died in this car?

44:48.126 --> 44:49.918
Clyde Barrow.

44:50.084 --> 44:51.293
Who?

44:51.459 --> 44:54.376
- Clyde Barrow and Bonnie Parker...
-Oh, yeah, yeah.

44:54.543 --> 44:55.751
Bonnie and Clyde.

44:56.793 --> 44:57.793
Get in.

44:58.793 --> 45:00.084
No fear, Nico, no fear.

45:13.584 --> 45:16.376
Bonnie Parker died
right where you're sitting.

45:17.501 --> 45:21.376
She had fifty bullet holes
in her body.

45:22.334 --> 45:25.959
Someone close to them betrayed them
and they fell into a trap.

45:31.834 --> 45:34.918
If I fall into a trap
like Bonnie and Clyde,

45:36.668 --> 45:37.709
that's no good.

45:39.876 --> 45:41.709
That's why I have to trust

45:41.876 --> 45:44.084
everyone near me.

45:46.459 --> 45:49.459
So, if you see anything strange
around here,

45:49.626 --> 45:51.334
you come and tell me, ok?

45:52.501 --> 45:54.668
Not a word to anyone.

45:54.834 --> 45:56.543
Not even Maria.

46:00.834 --> 46:02.543
Understand?

46:07.459 --> 46:09.334
I understand.

46:11.084 --> 46:13.251
<i>Feind hiort mit.</i>

46:14.293 --> 46:15.543
The enemy's listening.

47:17.001 --> 47:18.043
Hi.

47:26.334 --> 47:28.126
You didn't sleep all night.

47:28.793 --> 47:29.918
Everything's ok?

47:35.626 --> 47:37.459
Let's go back to the beach.

47:39.501 --> 47:43.126
Please. I miss that life, Maria.

47:44.418 --> 47:45.793
Trust me, let's go back there.

47:47.001 --> 47:49.084
I thought you loved it here.

47:49.251 --> 47:53.043
It's just so different.
Go with me, please.

47:57.418 --> 47:58.959
This is my family, Nick.

48:06.834 --> 48:08.334
What is it, Nick?

48:11.168 --> 48:12.418
You are not happy with me?

48:13.876 --> 48:15.001
You want to leave me?

48:15.168 --> 48:16.168
No.

48:17.293 --> 48:20.876
Maria, I can't even imagine
a life without you.

48:21.043 --> 48:22.376
Then what is it?

48:24.001 --> 48:25.709
Everybody loves you here.

48:30.834 --> 48:32.459
You're part of my family.

48:50.918 --> 48:53.793
Nico.
