<i>This operation</i>

49:42.751 --> 49:45.293
<i>is having significant results</i>

49:45.459 --> 49:49.043
so we need to have the national
public and armed forces support it.

49:50.376 --> 49:53.126
<i>This will give you
an idea of the magnitude</i>

