First, the Minister of Justice
lied when he said that...

50:07.543 --> 50:11.126
Pablo Escobar had a criminal record
in the United States.

50:11.293 --> 50:13.626
- Hello, Nick.
-Hello.

50:13.793 --> 50:14.918
Hello, Nico.

50:16.334 --> 50:19.668
As you can see we're moving everyone
out of the Hacienda.

50:19.834 --> 50:23.168
For a little while. You and Maria
will go to your brother's

50:23.334 --> 50:25.459
until we find you a place in Medellin.

50:29.043 --> 50:32.376
Drago will show you how to use
everything inside this bag.

50:54.501 --> 50:55.543
What is this?

50:59.709 --> 51:02.543
-It's for self defense, Dylan.
-Are you shitting me?

51:03.709 --> 51:05.334
I don't want a gun in my house!

51:08.084 --> 51:09.418
What is it?

51:10.168 --> 51:12.293
Is it the money? ls it?

51:14.293 --> 51:16.626
Is it really worth it
to become like them?

51:17.376 --> 51:18.584
I'm not like them.

51:20.751 --> 51:22.709
You're breaking my heart, man.

51:25.126 --> 51:28.293
I don't want Anne
to know anything about this.

51:28.668 --> 51:32.501
So, you make something up,
you pack your bags and you leave.

51:33.543 --> 51:35.001
Don't make a scene.

51:35.459 --> 51:37.668
Guys! Come to the radio!

51:37.834 --> 51:39.876
The Minister of Justice
has been killed.

51:50.501 --> 51:52.293
They say it was Pablo.

51:55.001 --> 51:58.209
They say that
he's declared war on the government.

52:37.459 --> 52:38.876
This is your bedroom.

