You don't touch it.

52:50.209 --> 52:52.709
He needs to keep moving
around these days.

52:52.876 --> 52:55.584
But don't worry,
this war will soon be over.

52:55.918 --> 52:58.126
- Are you done with the cash?
-lt's all done boss.

52:58.293 --> 53:01.001
Let's <i>go!</i> Let's <i>go, chiquitin!</i>

