No. Definitely not.

57:04.168 --> 57:05.501
What are you waiting for, Nico?

57:06.084 --> 57:08.751
Attack. Attack, Nico, attack.

57:08.918 --> 57:10.251
We're working on it.

57:11.668 --> 57:13.793
He's working on it.

57:14.376 --> 57:17.626
Shouldn't be work,
Nick, shouldn't be work...

57:21.501 --> 57:23.918
Your brother has a kid, hum?

57:24.251 --> 57:26.709
Yeah.
And they're expecting another one.

57:27.251 --> 57:28.668
You can do it.

57:31.376 --> 57:32.626
They're actually

57:33.418 --> 57:35.418
thinking about going back to Canada.

57:36.876 --> 57:40.209
She's kind of homesick
and wants to go back there.

57:43.626 --> 57:45.584
I want to ask you,

57:45.793 --> 57:48.834
I think that it might be good
for me and Maria to go back too.

57:50.084 --> 57:52.709
At least for a little while,
until things cool off around here.

57:53.376 --> 57:56.043
That's not a good idea, Nico. Not now.

58:00.001 --> 58:01.334
Does Maria know about it?

58:02.501 --> 58:04.959
Yeah, we talked about it.

58:09.334 --> 58:12.251
It's because
they're hitting like goats.

58:19.709 --> 58:22.501
Why does your brother wanna go back?

58:22.668 --> 58:24.584
Has he been having trouble
at the beach?

58:24.751 --> 58:27.834
No, that's all over, thank God.

58:28.918 --> 58:29.959
Thank God?

58:32.959 --> 58:34.251
What do you mean thank God?

58:36.626 --> 58:39.209
Nothing. Just a figure of speech.

58:40.793 --> 58:42.168
Ok.

58:46.543 --> 58:48.418
'Cause God has done
nothing to do with it.

58:50.501 --> 58:52.584
It was you, Nick.

58:55.959 --> 58:58.876
It was your intervention
that got those people killed.

59:01.626 --> 59:03.626
You're as guilty as I am.

59:13.293 --> 59:15.584
Camillo,
can you come help me with this?

59:15.751 --> 59:16.793
Sure.

59:17.876 --> 59:19.793
Nick, we forgot the salt.

59:33.959 --> 59:35.751
Thanks so much for doing this.
