if you don't know anything about him.

01:00:29.043 --> 01:00:31.376
We're all making sacrifices, Nico.

01:00:32.168 --> 01:00:34.251
And I'm very proud of you.

01:00:37.459 --> 01:00:39.209
You're like a son to me.

